title: Rory O'Sullivan
text: Rory O'Sullivan (born 25 July 1998 in <a href="Australia">Australia</a>) is an <a href="Australian">Australian</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who plays for the in <a href="Global%20Rapid%20Rugby">Global Rapid Rugby</a> and the <a href="Super%20Rugby%20AU">Super Rugby AU</a> competition. His original playing position is <a href="Scrum-half%20%28rugby%20union%29">scrum-half</a>. He was named in the Force squad for the Global Rapid Rugby competition in 2020.
